Package com.github.tadukoo.util.view.gradient

Class GradientBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.github.tadukoo.util.view.gradient.GradientBuilder
Direct Known Subclasses:
LinearGradient.LinearGradientBuilder, RadialGradient.RadialGradientBuilder
public abstract class GradientBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
Gradient Builder is an abstract builder for a Gradient to be extended by subclasses for making more specific Gradients, e.g. LinearGradient.
